        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_OSIK" id="위험분석-개념">위험분석 개념<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/pm/risk-analysis/#%EC%9C%84%ED%97%98%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
